# Intelligence Ask (`touch-intelligence`)

## When to Use
- Ask AI directly in CoreBox and copy responses fast.

## Trigger
- Feature ID: `intelligence.ask`
- Commands: `ai / @ai / /ai`

## Core Capabilities
- AI Q&A: ask directly in CoreBox and copy the response.
- Conversation handoff: CoreBox turns are linked to an Intelligence Session with a recoverable `handoffSessionId`.
- Supported platforms: `win32, darwin, linux`

## Config & Data
- Config/data files: None (handoff context is maintained by the Intelligence Session runtime)
- Plugin directory: `plugins/touch-intelligence`

## Permissions
- Required: `intelligence.basic`; Optional: `clipboard.write`

## Quick Start
1. In CoreBox, type `ai`.
2. Press Enter on the action you need.
3. Grant permissions when prompted.
